text: Jason Cunningham (born 26 September 1989) is an English professional boxer. He held the Commonwealth bantamweight title in 2015; the Commonwealth featherweight title in 2017; and challenged once for the British super- flyweight title in 2015. ==References== ==External links== * *Image - Jason Cunningham Category:1989 births Category:English male boxers Category:Living people Category:Sportspeople from Doncaster Category:Bantamweight boxers Category:Super-flyweight boxers Category:Flyweight boxers
